data.description: Wonderful open concept townhome in South San Diego! With a spacious layout and a large center island, it seems like the perfect place for entertaining. The proximity to the beach and Coronado is definitely a plus for those who enjoy coastal living. The convenience of being near the 905 and 805 freeways makes it easy to access other parts of the city. The growing area has a lot to offer in terms of amenities and community features. If you're interested in this townhome, it's definitely worth checking out!
